thread.title: Bojana
thread.title_full: Muscle Meals Direct reviewed by Bojana

author: Bojana
title: Bojana
text:
Food taste wonderful, I really enjoyed a my meals! One of the best prep food companies that I ever tried! Only thing that athletes at the Arnold Classic Australia can complain is the late delivery....we all nedded food early Thursday and food arrived late afternoon. It is very important thing if we are know that all athletes was 2 days out and diet plan should be followed strictly...international athletes was completely dependable on food they ordered.
Everything else is excellent!
